<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/default.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/responsive.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/fontkit/stylesheet.css">
    <!-- Latest compiled and minified CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <!-- Optional theme -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css" integrity="sha384-rHyoN1iRsVXV4nD0JutlnGaslCJuC7uwjduW9SVrLvRYooPp2bWYgmgJQIXwl/Sp" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- Latest compiled and minified JavaScript -->
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-Tc5IQib027qvyjSMfHjOMaLkfuWVxZxUPnCJA7l2mCWNIpG9mGCD8wGNIcPD7Txa" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kunst im Kinderzimmer</title>

    <style>
        .content-heading {
            margin-top: 0px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .language {
            margin-top: 90px;
        }
        .content-tablet {
            display: none;
        }
        .content {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-left: 75px;
        }
        .line-bottom {
            margin-top: 150px;
        }

        /**Mobile and XS-Screens**/
        @media only screen and (max-width: 767px) {
            .banner {
                margin-left: 50px;
                margin-bottom: 0px;
                width: 85%;
            }
            .content {
                display: none;
            }
            .content-tablet {
                display: block;
                margin-left: 2px;
            }
            .content-heading {
                margin-left: 2px;
                margin-top: 50px;
                font-size: 40px;
                text-align: left;
            }
            .content-text{
                margin-left: 0px;
                text-align: left;
                font-size: 18px;
                line-height: 1.48;
            }
            .line-bottom {
                margin-top: 100px;
            }
            .language {
                margin-top: -70px;
                margin-left: 610px;
            }
            .thin-font a{
                color: #303030;
            }
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 479px) {
            .banner {
                margin-left: 40px;
                margin-bottom: 0px;
                width: 65%;
            }
            .language {
                margin-top: -70px;
                margin-left: 70px;
            }
            .content {
                display: block;
                margin-left: 0px;
            }
            .content-text {
                margin-left: 0px;
                text-align: left;
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 1.48;
            }
            .content-heading {
                font-size: 32px;
                margin-left: 0px;
                margin-top: 50px;
                text-align: left;
            }
            .content-tablet {
                display: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="navigation-mobile">
    <button class="menu-button">Menu</button>
    <div class="menu-content">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/collection">Sammlung</a>
        <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
        <a href="/authors">K&uuml;nstler</a>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="language thin-font row">
    <div class="col-sm-9">&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"><a style="color:#de202c;" href="">DE</a>/<a href="">EN</a></div>
    <div class="col-sm-2">&nbsp;</div>
</div>

<div class="banner">
    <img class="banner" src="banner.png">
</div>

<div class="navigation default-font row">
    <div class="col-sm-5">&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="col-sm-1">&nbsp</div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"><a href="/">Home</a></div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"><u><a href="/collection">Sammlung</a></u></div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"><a href="/blog">Blog</a></div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"><a href="/authors">K&uuml;nstler</a></div>
    <div class="col-sm-2">&nbsp;</div>
</div>

<hr class="line-top"/>

<div class="content default-font row">
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    <div class="col-xs-8 col-md-10">
        <div class="content-heading default-font">Sammlung<br/></div>
        <div class="content-text default-font">
            Diese internationale Sammlung von KünstlerBilderBüchern besteht aus Zufallsfunden in Spezialbibliotheken,<br/>
            Buchhandlungen, Antiquariaten, Archiven und Museen, in Büchern über Kunst und Künstler oder auch durch<br/>
            persönliche Kontakte. Sie umfasst einen Zeitraum von über 100 Jahren und Künstler aus mehr als 20 Ländern.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
</div>

<div class="content-tablet default-font row">
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    <div class="col-xs-11">
        <div class="content-heading default-font">Sammlung<br/></div>
        <div class="content-text default-font">
            Diese internationale Sammlung von KünstlerBilderBüchern besteht aus Zufallsfunden in Spezialbibliotheken,
            Buchhandlungen, Antiquariaten, Archiven und Museen, in Büchern über Kunst und Künstler oder auch durch
            persönliche Kontakte. Sie umfasst einen Zeitraum von über 100 Jahren und Künstler aus mehr als 20 Ländern.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="books row">
        {% for i in 1..9 %}
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
                  <img src="/file/{{ i }}" width="180" height="250"/><br/><br/>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</div>


<hr class="line-bottom"/>
<div class="contact-impressum default-font"><a href="/contact">Impressum&nbsp;/&nbsp;Kontakt</a></div>
